Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:04.47,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to acquire a large sum of \Nmoney, I'll have to hunt bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.16,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,The question is how I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:16.37,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the circumstances, I could \Nend up facing multiple bandits at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.08,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I won't be \Nattacking a distracted opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:24.00,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Am I strong enough to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.08,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,No, I {\i0}have{\i1} to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:27.51,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Job Settings.
