Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:35.97,Status Text,SIGN LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(171,104)}Kaga Michio
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:29.66,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've got more new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.00,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,How's Warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:35.97,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(406,80)\fscy150}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hWarrior: Lv 1\N Effects: Minor Endurance Increase\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hTiny HP Increase\N\h\h\h\hSkill: Rush
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.97,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It has stronger effects than \NVillager, and it's got a skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:38.43,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep Hero, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.43,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs20\c&HD6DBDF&\an8\pos(300,142)}Explorer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.43,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs20\c&HD6DBDF&\an8\pos(300,206)}Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.43,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs20\c&HD6DBDF&\an8\pos(300,274)}Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:43.43,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Given what I'm about to do, \Nthis is the best setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:49.73,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, I'll be walking.
