Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.63,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,None here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.98,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,But having access to Identify \Nis a huge advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:44.44,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell at a glance who's a bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.64,Main,VILLAGER A,0000,0000,0000,,The bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.82,Main,VILLAGER B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Word is, they're being \Ntaken out one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:51.15,Main,VILLAGER A,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're getting revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.59,Main,VILLAGER A,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably those guys who were \Nchased out of the slums to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.65,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,The slums?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:59.53,Flashback,SOMARA,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Michio, try not to look around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.21,Flashback,SOMARA,0000,0000,0000,,There are some unsafe areas around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:07.79,Flashback,SOMARA,0000,0000,0000,,There are brothels, as well, \Nbut I wouldn't recommend going inside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.25,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.30,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs40\pos(320,314)\shad1.54\4a&H40&\frz3}The Slums
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.80,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,The air here is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.32,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like sewage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:25.22,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to being the \Nendpoint of the sewer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.66,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,it's also where outcasts and wretches end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.60,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.10,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\move(8,148,112,148)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.10,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\move(316,172,420,172)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.10,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(596,130,700,130)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.71,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.66,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Are they being cautious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:39.14,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose bandits wouldn't boldly \Nwalk around in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:41.33,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,This stench alone is going to make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.59,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.37,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check it out again at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:57.50,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped becoming depressed even \Nafter repeated uses of Teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:01.26,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Must be because of the levels \NI gained fighting that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.00,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I turned that potential \Ndisaster into good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:08.26,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to handle some \Nbandits even if the worst happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.41,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Time to resume exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.96,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,Going back into the labyrinth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.21,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Hold onto my key for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.44,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.18,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,You're working hard, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:24.07,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a lantern?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.72,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I borrowed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.17,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It only illuminates the area right around \Nmy feet, but it's better than not having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.09,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time out \Non the town at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.42,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything different at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.53,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.93,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\move(194,70,144,70)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.93,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\move(358,100,308,100)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.93,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\move(640,134,590,134)}Warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.93,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\move(159,230,253,230)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.93,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\move(374,130,468,130)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.93,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\move(496,150,590,150)}Villager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.92,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Still no bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.35,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they'd be around \Nat night. Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.50,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.69,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs40\shad0\4a&H40&\pos(320,300)}Red Light District
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.82,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally different from the \Nred light district during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.17,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,The lights at night make it \Nseem so much more dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.96,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.34,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.70,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I could get ripped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.22,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't imagine there's anyone \Nhere as beautiful as Roxanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.01,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Not entering a shop is the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:50.81,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.41,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(130,138)}Bandit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.10,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.30,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely heading towards the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.67,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Are there no other bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:24.65,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.07,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(150,150)}Bandit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.07,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(294,126)}Bandit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.07,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(402,234)}Bandit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.07,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(470,214)}Bandit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.07,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(548,165)}Bandit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.45,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If there are lookouts posted outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.16,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,then that single-story house must \Nbe the bandits' headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:34.98,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.00,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we've got Hugo to thank for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.44,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Did he just say Hugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:52.20,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I think the bandit boss I beheaded \Nin the starting town was Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.59,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\pos(58,97)}Identify
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.59,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,136)\b1\1a&H20&}Hugo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.59,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fs12\1a&H20&\pos(222,30)}<Male 38 Years Old>\N Thief: Lv 41\N Equipment: Iron Sword\N Thief's Bandanna\N Iron Armor\N Leather Boots
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:57.47,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Which means he's one of the remaining \Nbandits who were chased out of town
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.48,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,or an associate of Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.48,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do more research.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.98,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\pos(320,150)\c&HFFFFFF&}2 Days to\NPurchase Roxanne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:08.98,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm starting to get a sense \Nof what this town's like at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.36,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps because people \Ntypically stay overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.82,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,the businesses in the red \Nlight district close early,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.37,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,starting with shops that attract customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.57,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Then the bandits come out to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:25.19,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Like guards, they either patrol the town \Nand stand at crossroads or carouse at bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.95,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Even the bandits must have \Ngroups and territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.51,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,And they avoid interacting with \Neach other to an unnatural degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:38.71,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,That guy who was standing in basically \Nthe same place yesterday is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:43.27,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much, but this area must be his.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.21,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I hunted his group,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:50.53,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,the other groups would see it as someone \Nelse's problem and wouldn't make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:57.87,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If individual groups avoid interacting \Nwith each other, then I can make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:01.25,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord4\3a&H88&\c&HFFFFFF&}Vale\NVale Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.14,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:07.13,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,You were out late in the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.46,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,Have something to eat. \NIt's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.26,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,The murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.54,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,Those murders, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:19.67,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,There's a power struggle between the bandits \Nwho live in the slums of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.77,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.77,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.23,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,Between you and me, that's made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.28,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.77,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,A little while ago, there was a change \Nin leadership within a certain group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:36.49,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,There was a succession dispute and the \Nlosing faction was run out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.84,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,There are bandit factions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.37,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,The men who were killed the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:45.22,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,were bandits who won the succession \Ndispute and remained in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.63,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,but they're being targeted \Nby other groups, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.72,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,So they're making it look like \Nthe work of the banished bandits
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.49,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,and using this opportunity to take them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.88,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.55,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,There might be some trouble \Nover in the slums,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:02.17,Main,INNKEEPER,0000,0000,0000,,but this area is safe, under the \Nwatchful gaze of the knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:10.52,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I avoided entering the bandits' hideout \Nwithout knowing what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:15.44,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If I end up talking to the bandits, \Nthen it'll be easier to work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.85,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Roxanne...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:25.87,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Her branches so heavy with enormous fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:32.17,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll peel them ever so gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.09,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,And taste them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.51,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,They're hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.78,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sho harf...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:53.44,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I was so nervous, I didn't get much sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.36,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,But now's a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.40,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my Thief's Bandanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.50,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I can equip Durandal anytime, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.50,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\pos(320,150)\c&HFFFFFF&}1 Day to\NPurchase Roxanne
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:10.13,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs40\pos(320,314)\shad1.54\4a&H40&\frz3}The Slums
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.81,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,You got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.24,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.88,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,No one suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.47,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely extremely suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.27,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.68,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:30.58,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the information I want, \Nand it's yours for one gold coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.65,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,One, huh? \NWhat do you want to know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.36,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,He's interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:39.39,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true that bandits will \Nshell out 10 to 20 thousand nars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.78,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.62,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, our brother Hugo was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.12,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The man's dead, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.88,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me more about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.04,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.62,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:05.47,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,His allies must be in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.47,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:12.12,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss knew Hugo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:15.53,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping right now, but you \Nshould introduce yourself later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.61,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.64,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,The money's in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:20.43,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Can we talk in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.24,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:21.91,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.79,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. \NI'll give you the money here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:39.46,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,First, could I confirm that's \Nreally a Thief's Bandanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.56,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get a good look at it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:42.34,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:52.24,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,There was a succession \Ndispute a short while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.68,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,He was supposed to take over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:12:00.32,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,but some other factions joined \Nforces and drove him out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:06.17,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,They say Hugo attacked some \Nvillage after that and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.33,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.04,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in trying to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.37,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody saw me bring you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.44,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where you got that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:20.01,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,but with a Thief's Bandanna, \NI could get even more done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.53,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.68,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,So this was your intention from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.80,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.47,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,Bah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.03,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a weapon. \NWhat do you think you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:33.69,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll give you this bandanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.30,Main,LV9 BANDIT,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.70,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.42,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Two in the back, two in front.
