Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs6\pos(57,50)}Nina
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(152.667,88.667)\fs8}<Female 28 Years Old>\NThief: Lv 14
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs6\pos(206.666,199)}Identify
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs6\pos(195.666,222)}Evan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs8\pos(291.333,260.667)}<Male 36 Years Old>\NThief: Lv 38
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs6\pos(480.666,170.333)}Identify
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs6\pos(469.666,193.333)}Nora
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs8\pos(565.333,232)}<Female 24 Years Old>\NThief: Lv 11
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs6\pos(458,37.666)}Identify
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs6\pos(447,60.666)}Conrad
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:18.40,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs8\pos(547.334,102)}<Male 34 Years Old>\NThief: Lv 35
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:18.40,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,None of them are exceptionally \Nhigh level. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.36,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,His legs are down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.82,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Which means his head's up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:30.63,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly, so he doesn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.98,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Is his neck around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.71,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by all the blood, \NI must've cut an artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:44.44,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,He's a level 38 bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:46.78,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's a decent bounty on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:51.60,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:56.81,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Even if something unexpected occurs, \Nworst case, I can teleport out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.63,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! She made a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:02.62,Main,NORA,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:16.11,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,The last one noticed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:16.96,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:21.17,Status Text,SIGN LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304.667,120)\c&H9E9D9B&}Identify
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:21.17,Status Text,SIGN LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(286.667,152.667)\c&H7D8078&}Conrad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:21.17,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(428,118)\c&H9E9D9B&\b1}<Male 34 Years Old>\NThief: Lv 35\N{\1a&HFF&\t(730,771,1 \1a&H00&)}Equipment: Copper Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.74,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,This puts me at a disadvantage. Teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.93,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,He'll assume I'm still inside \Nthe room and call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.00,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I need to time my movements with the door's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.39,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to screw this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.37,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.06,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:51.38,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,His left hand is the one I'm holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.95,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Did the other bandits notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.31,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't detect any more \Nbandits inside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:05.34,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be difficult to retrieve \Nthe female bandit's hand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.29,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Three is the most I can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.37,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take on any more risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.72,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport. To the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:21.91,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.60,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I finally did the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:33.67,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's probably because I'm low on \NMP from teleporting a bunch of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.27,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just defeat some monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:43.50,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I should be at max MP by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:48.92,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:55.72,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, killing bandits \Nshouldn't be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.28,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,This world is different \Nfrom the one I came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:03.27,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,There are no police, laws, \Nor human rights to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:08.88,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,This was my only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.05,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,The bandits won't make a fuss over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.60,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If word gets out that their \Nleaders were killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.59,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,the other bandits might come after them next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.37,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, how am \NI going to cash these in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.80,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I just recently claimed a bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:31.67,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If I bring more of these in back to back, \NI might attract the attention of the knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:34.24,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take their cards to another town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:38.18,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. What if they question me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:41.46,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,They might ask me about the circumstances \Nunder which I killed the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:46.19,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't they find it suspicious that I \Ndidn't bring them to my own town's knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.06,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.07,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,My head's all screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.01,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what will happen, \Nbut one thing's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:58.40,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It's looking more likely \Nthat I'll acquire Roxanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.95,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.75,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.46,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\pos(320,141)\c&HFFFFFF&}Last Day to\NPurchase Roxanne
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.66,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I slept better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.55,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:26.94,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I should minimize the number of people \Nwho recognize me, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.69,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be easier if I knew a knight \Nwho was familiar with the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.52,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.20,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,He was there when I claimed my first bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:39.87,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.11,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:45.08,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Some guys picked a fight with me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.30,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they were bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:49.34,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.71,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I fought back and killed them, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.43,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:57.81,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,May I take a look at your Intelligence Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:58.56,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.54,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Will of the swiftly flowing spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.67,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,steady breath of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.56,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Open Intelligence Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.23,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,All good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:13.90,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go examine these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:20.44,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't ask any questions. Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.94,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I had the same thought last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:26.70,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess that's how bandits \Nare regarded in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:31.72,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to confirm they \Nbelonged to three bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.18,Main,MALE KNIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them had bounties on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:36.55,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.51,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,That was easier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.35,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,How many gold coins did I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.27,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.09,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than seven in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:58.03,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,With the 33 gold coins and 228 \Nsilver coins I've already got,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.78,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I can buy Roxanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.79,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.89,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about all the silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.50,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.41,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:17.55,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring her to you right away. \NOne moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.42,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.93,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:33.65,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is Roxanne, the girl you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.63,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.58,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:49.97,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master. However, \NI must apologize to you for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.05,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:56.12,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to spring on me now that \Nshe was working with the slave trader?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:59.55,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Or that she didn't want me to buy her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:06.56,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,I believed you'd come for \Nme and waited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:10.78,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,But I doubted you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:13.48,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might not come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.79,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:21.95,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I don't deserve \Nto be purchased by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:27.95,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you shall \Nbe known as Melos-anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.00,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.33,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem. \NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:37.59,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.49,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Roxanne, go to the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.68,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Let us establish a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.85,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your Intelligence Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:54.94,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:54.94,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.20,Main - Top,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Will of the swiftly flowing spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.69,Main - Top,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,steady breath of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.79,Main - Top,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Open Intelligence Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:03.05,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I should've given up on \NRoxanne at least once, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.20,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'd be even.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:09.20,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I could've given \Nup on someone so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.20,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,The contract is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.79,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look each \Nother's Intelligence Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.42,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:25.26,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0\c&H000000&\3c&HB7C349&\bord2\alpha&H40&\pos(206,36)\fscx89\blur2\b1}Roxanne <Female 16 Years Old> Beast Warrior – Slave\N{\fscx100}Owner: Kaga Michio
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:25.26,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I can tell we've signed a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.26,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the slave trader \Nwasn't a con artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.04,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:37.19,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing on here I \Nwouldn't want you seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.27,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:44.65,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0\c&H000000&\3c&HB7C349&\bord2\alpha&H40&\fscx91\blur2\b1\pos(226.667,34.667)}Kaga Michio <Male 17 Years Old> Explorer – Free Man\N{\fscx100}Owned Slaves: Roxanne
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.72,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,My job is set to Explorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:45.28,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,So your card displays your first job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:49.28,Sign_Basic,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\3c&H6D7325&\shad0\c&H000802&\an8}Kaga Michio <Male 17 Years Old>\NOwned Slaves: Roxanne
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:49.28,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,And this shows that I own her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:53.70,Main - Top,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for purchasing one of our slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:53.70,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:58.36,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you are Roxanne's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.65,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:05.15,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I've acquired Roxanne.
